Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think my dad could endure\Nbeing branded a thief.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I guess my mom\Ndid suspect that he really did it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It made me want to stop\Nbelieving in people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought maybe I would feel better{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if I could just hate\Neither my mom or dad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But after years passed,\Nmy mom let it slip,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Why couldn't I believe him back then?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That made me want to keep\Nloving both of them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I realized that believing\Nin people was my strong point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:08.28,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ERASED
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Airi go in there before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's probably still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi! Can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heavy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't make it.\NI'm not strong enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never count on a manga artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're goin' down, non-stop!\NBrace yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, go out the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get Airi mixed up\Nin your business anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting the credit for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will Airi be okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that fire...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me he did that too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:56.22,Grab,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sachiko Fujinuma's Phone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Incoming Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}This is Satoru Fujinuma.\NStay right where you are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fire was set to target Airi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it looks like I did it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Airi slipped the phone to me\Nso the police couldn't see this message.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then he knew from the beginning\Nwhere Airi lived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He followed her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He may be closer than I think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll look for him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Either I get caught first{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or I find him first.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Koiwa. Koiwa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Please do not leave\Nany articles on the train...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.55,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COLUMBUS RECORDS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just\Nidentify yourself already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's Satoru Fujinuma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you are Satoru Fujinuma,\Nnice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet at a public place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't given you\Nmy name yet, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:04:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will when we meet tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you may have\Nmurdered Sachiko Fujinuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}KOHAKUTEI COFFEE SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Satoru. Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sawada, formerly of TV Ishikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved. You really are Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you resemble your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're on guard, but I didn't\Ntell anyone about this meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I didn't murder\Nyour mother either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't suspect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because she didn't raise\Nthe kind of son who would kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday I remembered\Nthat it was in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This keeps snowballing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:06:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My string of blunders\Nmakes me partially responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking it's your fault\Nafter the fact is just pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those are Sachiko's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I always liked them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we talk about her phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:23.83,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COIN LAUNDRY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sawada, do you remember?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The serial killings 18 years ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jun Shiratori is on death row,\Nbut he still claims to be innocent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just as Satoru said.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shiratori didn't do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I know who did.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's meet at Koiwa Station tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I should've asked her for the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we talk about a past incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About Kayo Hinazuki's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the night of March 2nd, 1988,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo was beaten by her mother\Nand her mother's boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and locked in the storage shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She froze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The police suspected Kayo's mother\Nand the boyfriend of hiding the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But sometime between 10\Nand 11 pm on the 2nd,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo disappeared from the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo's mother discovered\Nthe disappearance at 12:30 am on the 3rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She called your house and casually\Ninquired about Kayo's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jun Shiratori had taken her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The footprints made\Nby rubber boots around the shed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,matched Jun Shiratori's boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:39.70,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HOKKAIDO POLICE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The police went public\Nwith their version of the events.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shiratori knocked Kayo out\Nwith physical violence
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then photographed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He put her in the family\Nbusiness cold storage room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and used an atomizer\Nto speed up her death by freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When her temperature dropped\Nto 20 degrees, she was brain dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shiratori waited about 30 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when she had almost\Nzero chance of recovery,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:08:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then returned her frozen corpse\Nto the Hinazuki shed before sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki would never have done that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo Hinazuki, Hiromi Sugita,\NAya Nakanishi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shortly before those three disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there was a series of abduction\Nmurders in the next town over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit was quickly arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but like Jun Shiratori,\Nhe denied any wrongdoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Including your present circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do you notice a common link?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been ridiculed for years for being\Na weirdo freelancer reporter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who investigates crimes\Nthat have already been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, none of them are solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Both Kayo Hinazuki and Sachiko\Nwere murdered by the same bastard
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who gives the police another suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now he's in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's a crafty son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He buys time by framing someone else,\Nwhich reduces eyewitness testimony
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and changes the circumstances\Nat the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, the investigation gets\Nfurther and further away from himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is going overboard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So he tried to shut her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Fujinuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He won't be able to get at her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what about the high school girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is she an accomplice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She helped him kill the mother
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and once that was done,\Nhe tried to silence her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Getting that girl caught up\Nin his madness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi, you have nothing to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. A stalker went after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been terrified!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aunty, that's not what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame yourself. I'm sorry\Nthat we didn't notice anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not what you think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The police are after the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to be afraid of now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They've got it wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.13,Sign Right,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fugitive Suspect\NResponsible for Arson?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.13,Sign Left,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Suspect Targeted\NCo-worker's House (Chiba)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe they're going\Nafter Satoru for murder and arson.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's impossible...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who would believe me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A message was sent\Nfrom Sachiko's phone to that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,According to the news,\Nshe wasn't badly hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure she's still in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He plotted to help the investigation along\Nby framing you for arson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's part of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I was already a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he would target her,\NAiri Katagiri, just for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you think\Nshe was already his target?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In order to frame me\Nas my mother's murderer,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he had to find out what time\NI'd be home from my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So in the 24 hours plus\Nbetween my mother's sighting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of his attempted\Nkidnapping and her murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he went to the pizza shop\Nand looked at the shift schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi must have seen his face then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's even someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then he's someone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who could get behind the counter\Nat a pizza shop to look at the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We may be able to use\Nthis to reach the bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a report on the murders\Nfrom 18 years ago on my computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can take a look if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think Jun Shiratori suspects\Nhis own father of being the killer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Regarding an alibi and evidence,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's possible that his continued\Nrefusal to say anything{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that might incriminate his father\Nmade himself look even worse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That would be like Yuuki,\Nwho dearly loves his father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:12:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A classmate saw Kayo Hinazuki\Nand Jun Shiratori together three times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Satoru Fujinuma's testimony\Nwas deliberately ignored,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it seems much was made\Nof the other student's testimony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:16.06,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FINAL SUSPECT LIST
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:16.06,Clang,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jun Shiratori\NSeiichiro Shiratori\NIsao Ishidou\NShinji Sakashita\NTadashi Yanagida
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A list of suspects.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know any of these names\Nother than Yuuki and his father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there are only five?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The police guessed\Nthat Hiromi Sugita was murdered{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}after being mistaken for a girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From this, the police made up\Na final list of five suspects{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who weren't acquainted\Nwith Hiromi Sugita.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're doing folk dancing today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:31.70,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Hockey Club\N1988 National Champions
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriously?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't wanna hold hands\Nwith some ugly girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd much rather hold hands\Nwith you, Hiromi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}T-That's gutsy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know why Hiromi was murdered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He knew Hiromi was a boy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so he killed him to keep himself\Noff the list of suspects.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jun Shiratori was arrested after someone\Nin the neighborhood reported{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that he'd been talking\Nto a third-grade girl when she was alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Photos taken at the time\Nof Hiromi Sugita's death{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}were confiscated from Shiratori's\Nfood storage room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The police concluded that Jun Shiratori\Nhad pedophiliac tendencies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They also collected pedophilia-related\Npublications from his bedroom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That kind of stuff wasn't there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:19.41,Sign Right Large,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect Day for Pleasure\NPerfect Day for All You Can See\NStrawberry: Beautiful Girl Photo Album\NHigh School Girls' Uniform Reference Guide\NErotica
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:19.41,Sign Left,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Paper Craft
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all camouflage to draw\Nattention away from himself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The list of suspects\Nbefore Hiromi's death...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:23.83,Sign Center,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Previous Suspect List
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His name is on here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Katagiri, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}2F NURSES STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to visit,\Nbut is the restroom over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No vacancies...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}except for room 201.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I'm gonna spring a leak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please pardon my\Nbad manners, Airi Katagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not Satoru Fujinuma, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'm his friend, Sawada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Airi's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:13.01,Grab,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 6\NGrim Reaper
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm positive Satoru didn't do any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't kill his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And he didn't set a fire to target me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,During the fire, he came\Nto the house to rescue me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your manager saved you, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must be confused\Nafter inhaling all that smoke.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know\Nwhat they're asking you, Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but they think I may be an accomplice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not being believed\Nis what hurts the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I think\Nabout who believes in Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I think\NI should've gone after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you, Airi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shoot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I forgot to turn it off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:16.95,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Public Phone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank goodness! You had it on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah. I'm as good as new.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More importantly, can I see you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the usual place...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? No, stay away from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi, I can't have you—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right! I promise, I'll go alone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go! It's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And here I am...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She may have been speaking\Nto the real killer on the phone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Getting Airi involved\Nwill only make it worse for her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SHINJI
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:15:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not flying at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doing this gives it\Nwhat's called dynamic lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will it really fly now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It sure will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's true! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It went by the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's flyin' too far! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What's an adult doing here\Nat this time of day?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this how people thought of Yuuki?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As promised, I came alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ashamed for thinking\Nit might be a police trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I said that out loud!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You better think that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fugitive, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think this Nishizono guy is fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nishizono?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen him two or three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The manager treats him with respect
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and from the badge he wears,\NI'd guess he's a city councilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He would've been able\Nto see the schedule,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it's not unlikely\Nthat he knew where I lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've met him before, briefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:54.60,Sign Right Large,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PREVIOUS SUSPECT LIST\NJun Shiratori\NSeiichiro Shiratori\NIsao Ishidou\NShinji Sakashita\NMakoto Kawata\NSachiko Fujinuma
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nishizono?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He wasn't on the list.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A fake name?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But a city council member\Nwouldn't be able to use a fake name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think he targeted me\Nbecause I know his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:18:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit! It isn't coming together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The final piece won't fit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel,\Nbut you can't beat yourself up over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have unfinished business\Nfrom a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's an idea I had for a manga story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About a grim reaper
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who makes a scheduling mistake\Nthat results in the death of a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He struggles to put things\Nback the way they were,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but the more he acts, the more\Nother people involved suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he means\Nto do the right thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when he gets mixed up in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,other people get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you right now, Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think, Airi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For example, I'm not hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That stuff about other people is just\Nthe reaper's subjective impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think that grim reaper\Nshould have more faith in himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that what's in front of you\Nis all still in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The conclusion is still up ahead\Nand nobody knows what it is yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi, I'm really glad that we met today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I said that out loud!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Fujinuma, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Fujinuma,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're under arrest for murder\Nand attemped murder resulting from arson.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The suspect was apprehended at 4:50 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:43.63,Clang,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHIBA POLICE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He would never do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Either through being arrested or Revival,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was prepared to have my\Nrelationship with Airi disappear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And here it is, the last time I'll see her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The thing I should do right now is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:19:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:19:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they followed me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I promised\NI'd come alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to give Airi\Nwhat I wanted to give her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like she did for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What would a hero say at a time like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't it hard fighting all on your own?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi, you've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can still hang in there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because you believed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Airi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.61,0:20:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I trusted you.
